  c) Bei Weiterverbreitung (soweit gestattet) muss auf das
     Original-Repository verwiesen werden:
     https://github.com/HalloWelt42/TubeVault

ENGLISH:
  a) All copyright notices, author credits, license references, and
     SPDX identifiers in source files, documentation, and configuration
     may not be removed, modified, obscured, or made illegible.
  b) This applies in particular to:
     - The LICENSE file in the root directory
     - Copyright headers in source files (© HalloWelt42)
     - SPDX-License-Identifier in source files
     - Author credits in package.json, Dockerfile, and configuration
  c) Any redistribution (to the extent permitted) must reference the
